////////////Pwer Scrolls by Admin M///////////////////////// 
version 56b should work with 55r's 
This IS NOT an awsome script but i have been using it for along time now.
Any bugs i have found i have fixed if you find any please e-mail me at spawnofsosaria@hotmail.com 

First off add this next section to what ever monster you want to get the power scrolls off 



ON=@SPELLEFFECT 
IF (<act.brain>==0) && (RAND(500) == 0) // keep this number high!! 
IF (<ARGN>==28) || (<ARGN>==39) || (<ARGN>==47) // Field spells 
SRC.NEWITEM=random_ps2 
SRC.act.BOUNCE 
SRC.SYSMESSAGE @1153 You have received a Power Scroll for your valor! 
ENDIF 
ENDIF 


ON=@GETHIT 
if ( <src.memoryfindtype(memory_ipet).uid> ) && (RAND(100) == 0) // This section takes pets into consideration 
src.memoryfindtype(memory_ipet).link.newitem=random_ps2 
SRC.memoryfindtype(memory_ipet).link.BOUNCE <new> 
src.memoryfindtype(memory_ipet).link.sysmessage @1153 You have been Rewarded a Scroll of Power for your valor!. 
return 0 
ELSEIF (<act.brain>==0) && (RAND(100) == 0) // begining of player section 
SRC.NEWITEM=random_ps2 
SRC.act.BOUNCE 
SRC.SYSMESSAGE @1153 You have received a Power Scroll for your valor! 
ENDIF 

 


